msgid "science-fiction fandom"
msgstr "science-fiction fandom"

#: ../../S/science-fiction-fandom.rst:7
msgid "n\\."
msgstr "名詞"

#: ../../S/science-fiction-fandom.rst:9
msgid ""
"Another voluntary subculture having a very heavy overlap with hackerdom; "
"most hackers read SF and/or fantasy fiction avidly, and many go to ‘cons’ "
"(SF conventions) or are involved in fandom-connected activities such as the "
"Society for Creative Anachronism. Some hacker jargon originated in SF "
"fandom; see :ref:`defenestration`\\, :ref:`great-wall`\\, "
":ref:`cyberpunk`\\, :ref:`h`\\, :ref:`ha-ha-only-serious`\\, :ref:`IMHO`\\, "
":ref:`mundane`\\, :ref:`neep-neep`\\, :ref:`Real-Soon-Now`\\. Additionally, "
"the jargon terms :ref:`cowboy`\\, :ref:`cyberspace`\\, :ref:`de-rezz`\\, "
":ref:`go-flatline`\\, :ref:`ice`\\, :ref:`phage`\\, :ref:`virus`\\, "
":ref:`wetware`\\, :ref:`wirehead`\\, and :ref:`worm` originated in SF "
"stories."
msgstr ""
"ハッカー界と非常に大きく重なる、もうひとつの自発的なサブカルチャー。ほとんどのハッカーはSFやファンタジー小説を熱心に読み、多くが‘con’(SFコンベンション)に行くか、Society"
" for Creative "
"Anachronism(創造的時代錯誤協会)のようなファンダム関連の活動に関わっている。一部のハッカー用語はSFファンダムに由来する。\\ "
":ref:`defenestration`\\ 、\\ :ref:`great-wall`\\ 、\\ :ref:`cyberpunk`\\ 、\\ "
":ref:`h`\\ 、\\ :ref:`ha-ha-only-serious`\\ 、\\ :ref:`IMHO`\\ 、\\ "
":ref:`mundane`\\ 、\\ :ref:`neep-neep`\\ 、\\ :ref:`Real-Soon-Now`\\ "
"を参照。加えて、ジャーゴンの用語\\ :ref:`cowboy`\\ 、\\ :ref:`cyberspace`\\ 、\\ :ref:`de-"
"rezz`\\ 、\\ :ref:`go-flatline`\\ 、\\ :ref:`ice`\\ 、\\ :ref:`phage`\\ 、\\ "
":ref:`virus`\\ 、\\ :ref:`wetware`\\ 、\\ :ref:`wirehead`\\ 、\\ :ref:`worm`\\ "
"はSF小説に由来する。"
